quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,"Ka lipitsi tse mathang, tse hemeselang"
  100,2,Tseo maotong a tsona ho qobang litlhase
  100,3,Tse tsometsang tlhaselo ka matjeke
  100,4,E be li tsosa leroele khabong
  100,5,Li parola lebotho la lira ka lehare e le ngatana ng’oe
  100,6,Ruri! Motho o hloka teboho ho Mong`a hae
  100,7,E bile ke paki holim’a seo
  100,8,O lehala leratong la leruo
  100,9,Na ha a tsebe hore mohla mabitla a hlatsang likateng
  100,10,Se ka lifubeng tsa batho se tla behoa pepeneneng
  100,11,Letsatsing leo Mong`a bona U tlabe A tseba tsohle tsa bona